    "body": "Prepare release.\n\n- release targets: app (1.0.1), core (1.1.0)\n- released packages: workflow-app, workflow-core\n- updated changelogs: crates/app/CHANGELOG.md, crates/core/CHANGELOG.md\n\n## monochange Release Record\n\n<!-- monochange:release-record:start -->\n```json\n{\n  \"schemaVersion\": 1,\n  \"kind\": \"monochange.releaseRecord\",\n  \"createdAt\": \"[DATETIME]Z\",\n  \"command\": \"release-pr\",\n  \"version\": null,\n  \"groupVersion\": null,\n  \"releaseTargets\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"app\",\n      \"kind\": \"package\",\n      \"version\": \"1.0.1\",\n      \"versionFormat\": \"namespaced\",\n      \"tag\": false,\n      \"release\": true,\n      \"tagName\": \"app/v1.0.1\",\n      \"members\": [\n        \"app\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"core\",\n      \"kind\": \"package\",\n      \"version\": \"1.1.0\",\n      \"versionFormat\": \"namespaced\",\n      \"tag\": true,\n      \"release\": true,\n      \"tagName\": \"core/v1.1.0\",\n      \"members\": [\n        \"core\"\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"releasedPackages\": [\n    \"workflow-app\",\n    \"workflow-core\"\n  ],\n  \"changedFiles\": [\n    \"crates/app/CHANGELOG.md\",\n    \"crates/app/Cargo.toml\",\n    \"crates/core/CHANGELOG.md\",\n    \"crates/core/Cargo.toml\"\n  ],\n  \"updatedChangelogs\": [\n    \"crates/app/CHANGELOG.md\",\n    \"crates/core/CHANGELOG.md\"\n  ],\n  \"deletedChangesets\": [],\n  \"provider\": {\n    \"kind\": \"github\",\n    \"owner\": \"ifiokjr\",\n    \"repo\": \"monochange\",\n    \"host\": null\n  }\n}\n```\n<!-- monochange:release-record:end -->",
